line_1: The visionary saint no joy admits,
line_2: In vain for him kind nature pours her sweets;

line_1: His voice no touch of harmony admits,
line_2: Irregularly deep and shrill by fits:

line_1: And though the bride, now freed from school, admits,
line_2: Of pride implanted there, some transient fits;

line_1: No casual flights the dang'rous train admits,
line_2: But wits once authors, are for ever wits.
